@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jyoaxm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.exp(v0 + 0.98) / 0.98))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos((v1 + 0.99 - v0 + 0.78)))
    v2 = wp.abs(v2)
    tmp = 0.41
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    tmp = (v1 * (0.83 + (v1 + 0.86 * tmp + 0.14)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.81)))
    data[tid] = v0
